**Sorting Words by Similarity in TypeScript with Levenshtein distance algorithm**

This code provides a function for sorting a list of words by similarity to a single word using the Levenshtein distance algorithm in TypeScript. It includes a function for calculating the Levenshtein distance between two strings and a function for sorting the list of words based on their similarity to the single word. It can be useful for tasks such as spell checking, text prediction, and more.

    npm install
    npm run start

